## 為什麼從 Day 1 做
- 後期加 i18n = 重構痛苦
- 多語言 = 市場大 10x
- App Store ASO 加分

## i18next（業界主流）
```bash
npm install i18next react-i18next
```

```typescript
// i18n.ts
import i18n from "i18next";
import { initReactI18next } from "react-i18next";

const resources = {
  "zh-TW": {
    translation: {
      welcome: "歡迎",
      login: "登入",
      hello_name: "嗨 {{name}}",
      items: "{{count}} 個項目"
    }
  },
  en: {
    translation: {
      welcome: "Welcome",
      login: "Sign in",
      hello_name: "Hi {{name}}",
      items: "{{count}} item",
      items_plural: "{{count}} items"
    }
  }
};

i18n.use(initReactI18next).init({
  resources,
  lng: "zh-TW",
  fallbackLng: "en"
});

export default i18n;
```

## 用
```tsx
import { useTranslation } from "react-i18next";

function Home() {
  const { t, i18n } = useTranslation();

  return (
    <View>
      <Text>{t("welcome")}</Text>
      <Text>{t("hello_name", { name: "Luffysky" })}</Text>
      <Text>{t("items", { count: 5 })}</Text>

      <Button onPress={() => i18n.changeLanguage("en")} title="EN" />
    </View>
  );
}
```

## 偵測語言
```typescript
import * as Localization from "expo-localization";

const deviceLang = Localization.locale;  // "zh-TW"
const deviceLocales = Localization.locales;  // ["zh-TW", "en"]
```

## 日期格式
```typescript
import { format, formatDistanceToNow } from "date-fns";
import { zhTW, enUS } from "date-fns/locale";

const locale = i18n.language === "zh-TW" ? zhTW : enUS;

format(new Date(), "yyyy 年 MM 月 dd 日", { locale });
formatDistanceToNow(date, { locale, addSuffix: true });
// "3 小時前" / "3 hours ago"
```

## 數字 / 貨幣
```typescript
new Intl.NumberFormat("zh-TW", {
  style: "currency",
  currency: "TWD"
}).format(1234.5);  // "NT$1,234.50"

new Intl.NumberFormat("en-US", {
  style: "currency",
  currency: "USD"
}).format(1234.5);  // "$1,234.50"
```

## RTL（阿拉伯語 / 希伯來語）
